  Updating remote-id in metadata.xml

  18 Jun 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> check-0.9.13-r1.ebuild:
  Update dependencies to require guaranteed EAPI=5 or multilib ebuilds, bug
  #513718.

